<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>FreshSpark Cleaning Services</title>
<style>
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
}

body {
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333;
}

header {
    background: #0ea5e9;
    color: white;
    padding: 20px 0;
    text-align: center;
}

nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 10px;
}

nav a {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.hero {
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.6), rgba(0,0,0,0.6)), 
    url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581578731548-c64695cc6952');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 100px 20px;
}

.hero h1 {
    font-size: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.hero p {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.btn {
    background: #22c55e;
    color: white;
    padding: 12px 25px;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    display: inline-block;
}

.section {
    padding: 60px 20px;
    text-align: center;
}

.services {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
}

.card {
    background: #f4f4f4;
    padding: 20px;
    width: 280px;
    border-radius: 8px;
}

.card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.testimonials {
    background: #f9fafb;
}

.contact form {
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: auto;
}

input, textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 10px;
    margin: 10px 0;
}

button {
    background: #0ea5e9;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
}

footer {
    background: #111827;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    margin-top: 30px;
}

@media(max-width: 768px) {
    .services {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
    }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h2>FreshSpark Cleaning Services</h2>
    <nav>
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
    <h1>Professional Cleaning Services in USA</h1>
    <p>Reliable, Affordable & 100% Satisfaction Guaranteed</p>
    <a href="#contact" class="btn">Get Free Quote</a>
</section>

<section class="section" id="services">
    <h2>Our Services</h2>
    <div class="services">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Home Cleaning</h3>
            <p>Complete home cleaning with eco-friendly products.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Office Cleaning</h3>
            <p>Professional office and workspace sanitization.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Deep Cleaning</h3>
            <p>Thorough deep cleaning for kitchens, bathrooms & more.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section testimonials">
    <h2>What Our Clients Say</h2>
    <p>"Amazing service! My house looks brand new." – Sarah M.</p>
    <p>"Very professional team and affordable pricing." – John D.</p>
</section>

<section class="section" id="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>FreshSpark Cleaning Services has been serving homes and businesses across the USA with trusted and affordable cleaning solutions. Our trained staff ensures spotless results every time.</p>
</section>

<section class="section contact" id="contact">
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <form>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name">
        <input type="email" placeholder="Your Email">
        <textarea rows="5" placeholder="Your Message"></textarea>
        <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
    </form>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 FreshSpark Cleaning Services | All Rights Reserved</p>
</footer>

</body>
  </html>
